---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Lönelotsarna – Experts in wage formation and salary and pay equity reviews"
  description="We provide support in matters related to wage formation, job evaluation, and pay equity reviews. We also provide Lonelots - a user-friendly and cost free tool for job evaluation and pay survey."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <img src={`${base}/images/Lönelotsarna.jpg`} alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center text-white">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">
        Experts in wage formation and salary and pay equity reviews
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto text-white/90">
        We provide support in matters related to wage formation, job evaluation,
        and pay equity reviews. We also provide Lonelots — a user-friendly and
        cost free tool for job evaluation and pay survey.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-12 text-center">About us</h2>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
          The Lönelotsarna team is a group of consultants with extensive experience, specialised
          in wage formation, salary review and equal pay.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
          We are also a non-profit organisation working for equal pay by developing methods,
          raising awareness and driving the public debate on equal pay. We have developed the
          Lonelots tool for job evaluation and provide it free of charge. We also publish
          annual reports on the structural pay gap.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70">
          Marie Trollvik is the chairperson of the association.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Lonelots Tool -->
      <div class="border-t border-brand-red pt-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">The Lonelots Tool</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
          The Lonelots tool is a weighted multi-factor and gender-neutral job evaluation tool
          that you can download free of charge. The system is based on the main areas of the
          Swedish Discrimination Act — knowledge and skills, responsibility, effort, and working
          conditions, factors that are globally recognized as essential for defining equivalent work.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
          The tool consists of two parts: a job evaluation system to assess which work is equivalent
          and a pay audit tool that provides the tables and charts needed to map and analyse wages
          in equal and equivalent work.
        </p>
        <a href={`${base}/en/analys-lonelots`}
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-red font-medium hover:text-brand-red-dark transition-colors">
          Learn more and download
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Consultancy -->
      <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Consultancy</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
          Need support with the pay survey process, wage formation, or salary setting?
        </p>
        <a href="https://viaconsulting.nu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-red font-medium hover:text-brand-red-dark transition-colors">
          Visit Via Consulting
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Structural Wage Gap -->
  <section id="reports" class="py-20 bg-brand-gray">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 text-center">The Structural Wage Gap</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Structural wage differences refer to wage disparities between groups of women and men
        that cannot be explained by differences in job requirements, the complexity of the work,
        or the employees' performance and skills. Instead, these pay gaps may stem from value
        discrimination, meaning that certain occupations and tasks are considered less valuable
        or important, often those traditionally performed unpaid by women.
      </p>
      <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        We publish annual reports on the structural wage gap in Sweden. We do so by comparing
        occupations across sectors and assessing them using the Lonelots job evaluation tool.
      </p>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
        <a href={`${base}/documents/Stäng+lönegapet+och+säkra+välfärden.pdf`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block bg-white p-5 border-b border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-red">2024</span>
              <span class="ml-2 font-medium text-brand-text group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors">Stäng lönegapet och säkra välfärden!</span>
            </div>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-text/30 group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}/documents/Högt+värderat+låg+lön.pdf`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block bg-white p-5 border-b border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-red">2021</span>
              <span class="ml-2 font-medium text-brand-text group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors">Högt värderat – låg lön</span>
              <span class="ml-2 text-sm text-brand-text/50">(Highly valued – low pay)</span>
            </div>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-text/30 group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-brand-text/50 text-center text-sm mt-6">
        Reports are published in Swedish. <a href={`${base}/#rapporter`} class="text-brand-red hover:text-brand-red-dark">View all reports →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
        Want to know more about how we can support you, attend a demo or have other questions?
      </p>
      <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-2">
        Once a month we have an open demo of the Lonelots tool in Swedish.
        If you are not a Swedish speaker, contact us for a demo in English.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6">
        <a href="mailto:info@lonelotsarna.se" class="text-brand-red font-medium hover:text-brand-red-dark text-lg">info@lonelotsarna.se</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
